title: Updated Chic Community! High End Finishes!
posting_body: ['We believe the perfect apartment home should delight residents with a variety of exclusive amenities.', 'After all, who doesn’t enjoy a beach entry resort-style pool to swim or relax in, a convenient fitness center to unwind from a stressful day or inviting friends over to relax by the fire in our outdoor lounge?', 'Not to mention our Grand Prairie location is unsurpassed in outdoor activities.', 'Community Amenities...', 'Beach Entry Resort Style Swimming Pool', '2 Fire Pits', 'Outdoor Fitness Area', 'Picnic Areas', 'Indoor and Outdoor Lounge Areas', 'Large Dog Park', 'Multiple Grilling Stations', '2.7 Acre Private Pond with Walking Paths', 'Smoke Free Community', 'Fully Gated Community', 'Computer Center and Conference Room', 'Exercise Studio with WiFi Enabled Cardio Equipment, Weight Training Machines and Flat Screen TV', 'Brushed Stainless or Chrome Hardware', 'Polished Concrete Floors (Phase II) - selected apartments', 'Gourmet Kitchens with Granite Counters and Island', 'Designer Cabinets with Pantry and Drawers Galore', 'Under Cabinet Lighting', 'Framed or Back Lite Mirror in Bath(s)', 'Linen, Coat Closet and Patio Storage', 'Walk in Closets', 'Wood Inspired Flooring - selected apartments', 'Close Access to Lynn Creek Marina at Joe Pool Lake', "Near Cedar Hill State Park's 15 Miles of Trails or Hike Through the 1,200 Acres of Prime Mountain Landscape", 'Within Walking Distance to Joe Pool Lake.', 'Enjoy Lake Experience, Fishing and Boating', 'Please Call Desiree with DASH Realty', 'show contact info', 'Mention Ad 849']
